The paper presents an algorithm for approximating the majority opinion of a crowd through intelligent sampling, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
